Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你振作起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直消沉下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭基他們好像正停留在霧之海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河道正好轉向那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進就會經過他們附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也能瞭解一些情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願皮尼歐沒幹蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家都平安無事就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是海賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全艦團發佈非常警戒警報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向皮尼歐傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中校嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你很有精神 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了你的求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過畢竟身處這顆星球的另一面 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以由我動身前去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時需要進行通信管制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能到我這邊來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻回歸庫蓋爾隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海賊…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是逃吧 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說逃 往哪逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是有這大炮和破廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們來一發作為見面禮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰角OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 這樣總該有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道像雷一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢這麼對待我的寶物！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…破廢鐵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自即刻起回歸人類銀河同盟軍指揮之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！ 破廢鐵！
